<<set $passage to "kaiIntro">><<set $module to "Introduction">>
<div class="wrapper">
  <<include "header">>
    /* <h1 class="title top">Hello - it's Kai again</h1> */
  <main class="speaking">
 <h1 class="title ">Hello - it's Kai again</h1>

    <div class="text-wrapper">
      <p>  If you are listening to me that means you must have my Gift to you, and you must have found the codeword to get in, so someone must have listened to the phone message. Great work.</p>
      /* / */
      <p>Last time we spoke I introduced myself, and I told you some things about me. I told you that I work with Greenpeace and Coney and a bit about who Greenpeace and Coney are. </p>
    
      <p>I also told you that I'm a playful activist but I didn't really tell you what that means… </p>
      /* / */
      <p>Playful activists spark change through play.</p>
      <p>We do this through 'playfulness' - which is an attitude.</p>
      <p>It's a way of relating to the world, to systems, and to the act of making change - we play with them.</p>
      <p>We also spark change through the act of 'playing'.</p>
      <p>We create games or interactive experiences that ask questions, offer new solutions, and show the frank reality of how things are.</p>
      /* / */
      <p>Together in this project we’ll be playful activists making a piece of Playful Climate Activism. </p>
      /* / */
      <p>We’re going to be looking at Climate Change. </p>
      <p>Sorry, some people would like us to say Climate Change... but sometimes I find it hard to even get the words out of my mouth, because let’s be honest - it’s a Climate Emergency.</p>
      /* / */
      <p>Change sounds natural, or even reversible, like changing your height by growing just a little bit taller.  No, I’m kidding 5ft 6 suits me fine thank you, and what we’re really looking at is destruction. It’s a crisis. </p>
      <p>As we’re at the start of the project, let’s work out where we’re starting from. </p>
         <<button "next">><<set $prevpass to $passage>><<goto "CodewordMod3">><</button>>
    </div>
  
 

</main>
<<include "footer">>
</div>






