:: mod3intro [nobr]
<<set $passage to "mod3intro">><<set $module to "Module 3">>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <<include "header">>
    <main  class="speaking">
        <div class="text-wrapper">
<p>  You might have discussed how the planet is warming up because of human’s carbon emissions. You might have talked about cars, planes, or cows. </p>
/* / */
<p>You might have spoken about how the richest 10% of people cause half the world’s total CO2 emissions. </p>
<p>You may have spoken about eating vegan, pollution, Fridays for Future, Autumn Peltier, Net Zero by 2050, a target of 1.5 degrees, Greta Thunberg, Extinction Rebellion, Reduce, Reuse, Recycle... </p>
/* / */

<p>You might have talked about the Climate Emergency being complex, or about how it overlaps with so many other emergencies: the pandemic, the cost-of-living crisis…. </p>
/* / */
<p>You might not have said any of this, or you might have said a million other things. You’ll know totally different things from me, and probably more, and you’ll know so much more how the Climate Emergency affects you - where you live, where you go to school. </p>
/* / */
<p>
  We can see this emergency happening all around us. 
  History has taught us you don’t stand still in an emergency. You act. 
</p>
/* / */

<p>
  Before we think about action, we need to start by understanding how things are.
  And from the very beginning, we need to understand that the Climate Emergency is not isolated, it's not separate from other struggles. or violence, or destruction. It is all interconnected. 
</p>
/* / */
We’re going to hear from Dr Mya-Rose Craig and watch a video she made for Greenpeace.
Dr Mya-Rose Craig is a climate activist from the UK 
She’s great. 
/* / */

<p>Before the video though, I’m going to give a content warning. </p>
<p>Her video is about racism and environmental destruction.</p>
<p>This video is really honest</p>
<p>And you might find it hard to watch at points. </p>
<p>We’ll break it up though. </p>
<p>Take it step by step, together. </p>
<p>Teacher, please do speak to the class about what they might need whilst watching this video</p>
/* / */

<p>I'm going to hand over to Dr Mya-Rose Craig now – </p>
    
   <p> Click <<button "Move On">><<set $prevpass to $passage>><<goto "mod3vid">><</button>>when you are ready. </p>
   </div>
    </main>
         <<include "footer">>
  </div>






